Please join Jim Suttle and I in welcoming Roger Espinoza to the EOTT PLP team effective 16 June 01.  Roger will be part of the Midland area Pipeline Scheduling team reporting to Jim as Stream Quality Manager, West Texas and New Mexico.   

With Roger's experience in the industry and his familiarity with the EOTT assets in West Texas and New Mexico we expect him to bring substantial value to PLP and EOTT Energy.   He will spearhead our  Quality Management Program, an initiative designed to ensure on-spec quality coupled with the maintenance of the commercial value of the stream in our pipeline systems.